<h1>Notification styles</h1>
<p>This window is used to edit the appearance of <a href="../../../../../alvao-service-desk/implementation/services/notifications">
notifications</a>, for example to match your <a href="../../../../../alvao-service-desk/implementation/html-text-style">uniform corporate style</a>.</p>

<p>Options:</p>
	<ul>
 <li><strong>Notification Styles</strong> - edit the definition of CSS styles for notifications.</li>
  <li><strong>Restore Default</strong> - return the contents of the <em>Notification Styles</em> field to the default status after installing Alvao. </li>
 
	</ul>

</asp:Content>
